Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的啊 穆奇娜美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澜你好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小园
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆奇娜美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.55,0:00:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上咯 小绿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直像小猫咪似的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全靠了机体的性能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般的战斗机驾驶员已经不能和她们相比了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上原 告诉她们三个别冲上宇宙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过维拉朱利奥最近没有出现还真是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也不会就此罢休的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头儿 外部联络
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是法洛斯田所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是已经到了嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告知全体沃克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即返航
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返航
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 正准备露一手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快给我滚回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田所先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长马上就要来法洛斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的老大NOVUMUNDUS的会长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长？
